Subscribing to GLive? No Contest! ►►http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 

This was a special morning edition of GTLive! We got toasted playing I AM BREAD in Star Wars pajamas while wielding a knife all over the kitchen. It was...a little weird...but AWESOME! We had some connectivity issues with the internet during this one, so it's a little on the short side, but if you like what you saw and you want more I AM BREAD, let us know in the comments!
